>暴跌</b>更是家常便饭。\",\"cite\":\"12\",\"docTitle\":\"异质信念、卖空限制与股价行为 \",\"engSent\":\"Especially Chinese Stock market has been and is experiencing big bubble and <b>crash</b>.\",\"url\":\"http://www.cnki.net/kcms/detail/detail.aspx?CurRec=21&QueryID=1&dbcode=CDFD&dbname=CDFDLAST2010&filename=2009077571.nh\"}},{\"tr\":{\"nat\":\"金融危机\",\"chnSent\":\"当然，<b>金融</b>泡沫也常常会导致<b>金融危机</b>，所以需要测评<b>金融</b>泡沫的安全性。\",\"cite\":\"11\",\"docTitle\":\"经济全球化背景下的金融泡沫研究 \",\"engSent\":\"While financial bubbles may lead to <b>crash</b> from time to time, the instruments to test their safety are much demanded.\",\"url\":\"http://www.cnki.net/kcms/detail/detailall.aspx?dbcode=CDFD&dbname=CDFD9908&filename=2007069049.nh\"}}],\"num\":2}},{\"entry\":{\"major\":\"医药科学\",\"trs\":[{\"tr\":{\"nat\":\"事故\",\"cite\":\"9\",\"docTitle\":\"脊柱脊髓型严重多发伤大鼠急性期血流动力学及治疗过程中心血管反应性变化及其机制 \",\"url\":\"http://www.cnki.net/kcms/detail/detailall.aspx?dbcode=CDFD&dbname=CDFD2009&filename=2009023156.nh\"}}],\"num\":1}},{\"entry\":{\"major\":\"电子、通信与自动控制技术\",\"trs\":[{\"tr\":{\"nat\":\"事故\",\"chnSent\":\"然而，随着电力系统的不断发展，负荷迅速增加，远方电源供电比重增大，以致在负荷高峰时传输容量有可能接近极限，增加了出现电压崩溃并发展为全网性<b>事故</b>的可能性。\",\"cite\":\"2\",\"docTitle\":\"考虑电压稳定的无功优化研究及其实现\",\"engSent\":\"Although, when load increases quickly, the power from far has a large proportion, and so that the transmission capability is possibly close to the limit, which makes the possibility of voltage <b>crash</b> bigger.\",\"url\":\"http://cn.noteexpress.net/\"}}],\"num\":1}},{\"entry\":{\"major\":\"航空、航天科学技术\",\"trs\":[{\"tr\":{\"nat\":\"坠毁\",\"cite\":\"1\",\"docTitle\":\"通用飞机结构耐撞性分析与设计关键技术研究\",\"url\":\"http://cn.noteexpress.net/\"}}],\"num\":1}},{\"entry\":{\"major\":\"纺织科学技术\",\"trs\":[{\"tr\":{\"nat\":\"粗布\",\"cite\":\"0\"}}],\"num\":1}}]},\"syno\":{\"synos\":[{\"syno\":{\"pos\":\"n.\",\"ws\":[{\"w\":\"collision\"},{\"w\":\"precipitation\"},{\"w\":\"impact\"}],\"tran\":\"碰撞；崩溃；坠落\"}},{\"syno\":{\"pos\":\"vt.\",\"ws\":[{\"w\":\"fall of\"},{\"w\":\"fall to pieces\"}],\"tran\":\"坠